{
  "title": "Moist Brown Sugar Turkish Semolina Revani",
  "description": "A traditional Turkish dessert featuring brown sugar and semolina, with a moist and resinous texture, and a cheese-pull effect when sliced. This recipe is egg-free and perfect for meal prep.",
  "cuisine": "Turkish",
  "diet": [
    "vegetarian",
    "egg-free"
